# shellcheck shell=bash

set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
GnuCOBOL (formerly OpenCOBOL) is a free COBOL compiler that implements
substantial parts of COBOL 85, COBOL 2002, COBOL 2014, and COBOL 2023.

GnuCOBOL translates COBOL source code to C, then compiles it with a
native C compiler to produce executables.

Main command: cobc (the GnuCOBOL compiler)

For more information: https://gnucobol.sourceforge.io/
EOF
